About

Royall Design has been in existance since 2003.

  • 2003-2007

    Our Humble Beginnings

    Two graphic designers returned to Iowa after finishing their degrees in the Chicagoland area.

  • 2007

    An Agency is Born

    A local hair salon called on Royall Design to create their logo.

  • May 2015

    Transition to Full Service

    We started picking up more and more clients and needed time to persue our next avenues.

  • January 2016

    Phase Two Expansion

    We have always enjoyed designing and making prints to give as gifts, and we decided it would be ideal to sell them to the public.
